  <summary date="2021-11-16T12:46:14Z" status="Introduced in House">North Pacific Ocean Protection Act

This bill prohibits the Department of the Interior from issuing a lease for the exploration, development, or production of oil or natural gas in specified areas of the Outer Continental Shelf off the coasts of Washington, Oregon, and California.</summary>
